quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  37,77,"Men daɗndi ɓeynguure makko makko nden e gomɗimɓe mo ɓen tun. Ɓeya kan, Men yooliri ɓeya keeferaaku maɓɓe ngun."
  37,78,"Men heddinani mo e mofte hikkotooɗe ɗen, mantoore moƴƴere, nde ɓe mantirta mo."
  37,79,"Nuuhu hisii o daɗii wowleede bone, e mofte sakkitiiɗe ɗen. Wurin, mantoore e jantoore moƴƴere, heddoto fii makko."
  37,80,"Ko sugu ndii njoɓdi, ndi Men warjorii Annabi Nuuhu, woni ko Men warjorta moƴƴinooɓe dewe mun ɗen, ɓe rewi Alla tun."
  37,81,"Kanko Nuuhu, ko o jeyanooɗo e jeyaaɓe Amen gomɗimɓe, woni e ɗoftaare Alla ɓen."
  37,82,"Refti Men yooliri hedditiiɓe ɓen, waame mbo Men wurti e maɓɓe on. Ɓe fow maɓɓe ɓe gasi."
  37,83,"Awa Ibraahiima, ko jeyanooɗo e jokkuɓe diina makko, rewi laawol makko ka wootinɗingol Alla."
  37,84,"Janto nde o ardunoo ka Joomi makko, ɓernde hisunde e sirku, laaɓanɗo Alla e tagu Makko ngun."
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yimɓe mun sirkaynooɓe ɓen: Ko honɗum rewton gaanin Alla?"
  37,86,"E ko reweteeɗi fefindaaɗi, faalaɗon rewude ko wanaa Alla?"
  37,87,"Ko sikkuɗon, onon yimɓe am, e Joomiraawo tageefo ngon, si on hawroyii e Makko, hara on rewaano Mo? Ko sikkuɗon O gollata on ontuma?"
  37,88,"Annabi Ibraahiima ndaariri ka koode, himo taskoo ɗaɓɓa feere, no daɗira yaltidugol e maɓɓe."
  37,89,"O ngantinori yaltidugol e yimɓe makko ɓen ka iidi maɓɓe, wiide: ko mi nawnuɗo."
  37,90,"Ɓe acci mo caggal ɗon, ɓe hucciti."
  37,91,"O moltii e reweteeɗi maɓɓe ɗin gaanin Alla, o jalnori ɗi maakugol: E on ñaamataa ko sirkanooɓe on ɓen moƴƴinani on kon?"
  37,92,"Ko heɓi on, on wowlataa, on jaabotaako? Ko sugu ɗum ɗoo rewetee gaanin Alla?"
  37,93,"Ibraahiima moltorani ɗi, piyirgol ɗi junngo makko ñaamo ngon, fii muncugol ɗi."
  37,94,"Rewaynooɓe ɗin sanamuuji ɓen, fewri ka makko, hiɓe yaawno."
  37,95,"Ibraahiima fewtitiri ɓe tabitaal, o feli ɓe, o maaki: E on reway kon ko lesirɗon juuɗe mon, accon Alla?"
  37,96,"Ko Alla tagi on, O tagi golle mon ɗen, wano ɗin sanamuuji ɗi leston. Ko Kanko tun hanndi e Mo rewon, hara on renndidaani Mo e goɗɗum goo."
  37,97,"Nde ɓe ronkunoo teeɗoragol mo hujja, ɓe yahri doole, ɓe diisonsiri haa ɓe fottani ko ɓe waɗata ibraahiima; ɓe wi'i: mahanee mo maadi, hebbiniron ndi carma, huɓɓon ɗe yiite, refti buɗon mo ton."
  37,98,"Yimɓe Annabi Ibraahiima ɓen faandanii mo bone, no ɓe gaynira fii makko,ɓe ɓoortondira e makko, kono Men waɗi ɓe kamɓe sooyuɓe ɓen; nde Men waɗannoo mo yiite ngen ɓuuɓol e kisiyee."
  37,99,"Ibraahiima maaki: Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, mi yalta e leydi yimɓe am ɓen, no mi heɓira feere rewugol Mo; aray nde O fewnata lam e ko moƴƴanta lam aduna e laakara."
  37,100,"Joomi am, arsikam ɓiɗɗo moƴƴo, ko wallitoo lam, semmbina lam e yimɓe am ɓen, tuma mi ferata."
  37,101,"Men jaabiniri toraare makko nden, humpitugol mo ko welata mo, fewndo Men wewlinirnii mo geɗaljo mawnoowo, muññoytooɗo; on woni Ismaa'iila (yo o his)."
  37,102,"Nde Ismaa'iila mawnunoo, o yottodi e ben makko jahal, ben makko Ibraahiima hoyɗi, koyɗol Annabaaɓe ɓen non, ko wahayu. O humpiti geɗal makko wiide mo: ko an yo ɓiɗɗo am, mi yi'ii e koyɗol, wonnde miɗo hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'uɗaa e ɗum. Ismaa'iila jaabii baaba'en mun, wiide: Baaba'en, waɗee ko yamiraɗon kon fii hirsugol lam, on taway lam, si Alla jaɓii, jeyaaɗo e muñooɓe e weltorɓe ñaawoore Alla nden."